{
  "description": "A breathtaking view of a towering waterfall cascading down a sheer rock face, partially obscured by lush, vibrant green foliage in the foreground. The waterfall appears as a white, misty stream against the gray rock. The foreground is filled with branches and leaves, creating a natural frame around the waterfall. The leaves are a bright, almost neon green, suggesting spring or new growth. The rocks are weathered and dark, contrasting with the bright white of the water. The overall scene evokes a sense of power, serenity, and natural beauty.",
